Package explore3d.groups

Class Summary
DirGroup Transform group that puts DoorShapes, PanelShapes and LabelGroups together so that they form a wall with labeled doors for directories.
FileGroup Creates a left or right file wall using FileShape, LabelGroup and PanelShape objects.
LabelGroup Group of LabelShape objects
UpGroup Create panel with door to parent directory
